msgid "This utility should only be used in live mode!"
msgstr "Þetta tól ætti aðeins að nota í lifandi ham!"

msgid ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting correctly there are no "
"problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='12'>Þetta tól ætti að nota í lifandi ham og til að endurheimta Manjaro stígvélina\n"
"sett upp á HD eða SSD.</span> <span font='12' foreground='red'>Ef uppsett kerfi er að byrja rétt "
"eru engin vandamál í stígvélinni, svo það er\n"
"betra að halda ekki áfram að nota þetta tól.</span> <span font='10' foreground='gray'>Sennilega "
"einnig vinna með öðrum Linux dreifingum.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Viltu halda áfram?\n"
"\n"
"\n"

msgid "Restore Boot, Grub, Initrd and others stuff"
msgstr "Restore Boot, Grub, Initrd og fleira dót"

msgid "Wait..."
msgstr "Bíða..."

msgid "I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"
msgstr "Ég fann ekkert Linux uppsett á þessari tölvu, hætt við ferli."

msgid ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't find any EFI "
"partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"The stígvél í lifandi ham er að nota EFI ham, en <span foreground='red'>ég fann enga EFI "
"skipting</span> á þessari tölvu,\n"
"sennilega mun GRUB endurreisn ekki virka.\n"
"\n"
"Reyndu að endurræsa og í gegnum tölvuna BIOS gera stígvél í Legacy eða BIOS ham.\n"
"\n"
"Viltu reyna jafnvel þótt lítið sé líklegt að það virki?"

msgid ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Boot í lifandi ham er að nota Legacy ham, einnig kallað BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>en ég fann að minnsta kosti eina EFI skipting á þessari tölvu</span>,\n"
"sennilega mun GRUB endurreisn ekki virka.\n"
"\n"
"Reyndu að endurræsa og í gegnum tölvuna BIOS gera stígvél í EFI ham.\n"
"\n"
"Viltu reyna jafnvel þótt lítið sé líklegt að það virki?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Veldu valkost:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Ég fann fleiri en einn EFI skipting, veldu hver ætti að nota:"

msgid "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."
msgstr "Engin EFI skipting valin, hætt við ferli."

msgid "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "
msgstr "Endurheimta stígvél, ruðning og initrd "

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one should restore the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Veldu valkost:</span>\n"
"\n"
"Ég fann fleiri en einn Linux uppsett á þessari tölvu, veldu hver ætti að endurheimta stígvél:"

msgid "No selected partition, canceled process."
msgstr "Engin valin skipting, hætt við ferli."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"I found more than one storage device, select which one should record the boot:"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Veldu valkost:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"Ég fann fleiri en eitt geymslutæki, veldu hver ætti að taka upp stígvélið:"

msgid "Disk"
msgstr "Diskur"

msgid "Size"
msgstr "Stærð"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "Nafn"

msgid "Partition table"
msgstr "Skiptingartafla"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>    \n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span>  LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected disk:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk partition table:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk Size:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Staðfestu gögnin</span>: <span font='11' "
"foreground='gray'>Ræsihamur:</span> LEGACY / BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valinn diskur:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Diskur skipting borð:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Diskur stærð:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valin skipting:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valið kerfi:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Skiptingarsnið:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Skipting UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Viltu halda áfram?    \n"
"\n"

msgid "Your computer is not connected to the internet, options 2 and 3 need internet to work."
msgstr "Tölvan þín er ekki nettengd, valkostir 2 og 3 þurfa internet til að virka."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways (<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or "
"Complete</span>),if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Veldu viðeigandi valkost:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Endurreisn er hægt að gera á 3 vegu (<span foreground='gray'>Einfalt, millistig eða lokið</span>), "
"ef þú ert í vafa, reyndu það fyrsta\n"
"valkostur, endurræstu tölvuna og sjáðu hvort þú leystir.\n"
"\n"
"Ef vandamálið er viðvarandi skaltu prófa aðra valkosti."

msgid "Option"
msgstr "Valkostur"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Lýsing"

msgid "Simple, just record the grub again at the beginning of the disk."
msgstr "Einfalt, skráðu bara matinn aftur í byrjun disksins."

msgid ""
"Intermediate, reinstalls the GRUB package in the partition, generates the configuration and updates "
"Initrd."
msgstr "Millistig, setur GRUB pakkann aftur í skiptinguna, býr til stillingar og uppfærir Initrd."

msgid ""
"Complete, performs the stages of the intermediate restoration, updates the system and checks if the "
"LTS kernel is installed."
msgstr ""
"Ljúka, framkvæmir stig millistigs endurreisnar, uppfærir kerfið og athugar hvort LTS kjarninn sé "
"settur upp."

msgid "Interactive, opens a terminal within the selected system."
msgstr "Interactive, opnar flugstöð innan valda kerfisins."

msgid "Interactive, opens a TUI control center within the selected system."
msgstr "Gagnvirkt, opnar TUI stjórnstöð innan valda kerfisins."

msgid "Collect useful logs from installed system"
msgstr "Safna gagnlegum annálum frá uppsettu kerfi"

msgid "Interactive, opens the package manager within the selected system."
msgstr "Gagnvirkt, opnar pakkastjórann innan valda kerfisins."

msgid "Done!"
msgstr "Búinn!"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI partition:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Staðfestu gögnin</span>: <span font='11' "
"foreground='gray'>Ræsihamur:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI skipting:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valin skipting:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Valið kerfi:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Skiptingarsnið:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Viltu halda áfram?\n"
"    \n"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways(<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or Complete</span>), "
"if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Veldu viðeigandi valkost:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Endurreisn er hægt að gera á 3 vegu(<span foreground='gray'>Einfalt, millistig eða lokið</span>), "
"ef þú ert í vafa, reyndu það fyrsta\n"
"valkostur, endurræstu tölvuna og sjáðu hvort þú leystir.\n"
"\n"
"Ef vandamálið er viðvarandi skaltu prófa aðra valkosti."
